      "message": "Line 101: 🟡 Suggestions - `tokenBucket_ + bytesToAdd` can overflow before `std::min()` clamps it, producing a much smaller bucket after long idle periods or very high bandwidth limits. Clamp using subtraction from `maxBucket` before adding.\n```suggestion\nconst auto room \u003d maxBucket \u003e tokenBucket_ ? maxBucket - tokenBucket_ : 0;\ntokenBucket_ +\u003d std::min(bytesToAdd, room);\n```",
