      "message": "[Critical] Line 248: 🔴 Critical Issues - `std::static_pointer_cast\u003cvideo::VideoRtpSession\u003e(videoSession)` assumes every MEDIA_VIDEO RTP session is a `VideoRtpSession`. If another `RtpSession` subtype is ever present, this is undefined behavior. Use `dynamic_pointer_cast` and skip non-video RTP sessions.\n```suggestion\nfor (const auto\u0026 videoSession : thisPtr-\u003egetRtpSessionList(MediaType::MEDIA_VIDEO)) {\n    if (auto videoRtp \u003d std::dynamic_pointer_cast\u003cvideo::VideoRtpSession\u003e(videoSession))\n        videoRtp-\u003eonAudioCongestion(audioLoss);\n}\n```",
